## Stack

- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router) + React 19 + Tailwind CSS 4
- **Backend:** Supabase (Auth + DB + Storage + RLS)
- **Tests:** Vitest (unit/integration) + Playwright (E2E)
- **Deploy:** Vercel
- **Gestor:** PNPM

---

## Inicio rapido

```bash
# 1. Instalar dependencias
pnpm install

# 2. Copiar .env.example a .env.local y rellenar
cp .env.example .env.local
$EDITOR .env.local

# 3. Arrancar Supabase local (requiere Docker)
pnpm supabase:start

# 4. Arrancar el server de desarrollo
pnpm dev

# 5. Abrir http://localhost:3000
```

---

## Comandos

```bash
pnpm dev               # Server de desarrollo (con Turbo)
pnpm build             # Build de produccion
pnpm start             # Server de produccion local
pnpm test              # Tests unit + integration (watch)
pnpm test --run        # Tests unit + integration (single run)
pnpm test:e2e          # Tests E2E con Playwright
pnpm lint              # Lint
pnpm typecheck         # Type check
pnpm format            # Prettier
```

